Question Name: Delete Duplicate Emails
Language: MySQL
Difficulty: Easy
Topic: SQL, DELETE, Self Join

MySQL Solution

DELETE p1
FROM Person p1
JOIN Person p2
ON p1.email = p2.email
AND p1.id > p2.id;

